{"title":"列表和超链接","date":"2020-10-25T09:33:17.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2020年10月25日","L":"2020/10/25","MM-DD":"10-25"},"link":"posts/9a7f11f9","comments":true,"tags":["HTML5+CSS3"],"categories":["网页设计"],"updated":"2020-10-25T14:31:52.000Z","content":"<h1 id=\"列表标签\">列表标签<a href=\"#列表标签\" title=\"列表标签\"></a></h1><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/dxsummer/cdn/img/html/20201025173701.png\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" /><figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">ul</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">ul</span>&gt;</span>\t标签用于定义无序列表</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span>\t标签用于描述具体的列表项</span><br><span class=\"line\">每对<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">ul</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">ul</span>&gt;</span>中至少应包含一对<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span>。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id=\"无序列表-ul\">无序列表 ul<a href=\"#无序列表-ul\" title=\"无序列表 ul\"></a></h2><ul><li><p><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code>和<code>&lt;li&gt;</code>都拥有<code>type</code>属性，用于指定列表项目符号。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>不赞成使用无序列表的type属性，一般通过CSS样式属性替代。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>&lt;li&gt;</code>与<code>&lt;/li&gt;</code>之间相当于一个容器，可以容纳所有的元素。但是<code>&lt;ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</code>中只能嵌套<code>&lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</code>，直接在<code>&lt;ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</code>标签中输入文字的做法是<strong>不被允许的</strong>。</p>\n</li>\n</ul><div class=\"φcz\"><div class=\"φdb\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th><strong>type属性值</strong></th><th><strong>显示效果</strong></th></tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td>disc（默认值）</td><td>●</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>circle</td><td>○</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>square</td><td>■</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></div></div><blockquote>\n<p><strong>例</strong></p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n    <li  type=\"square\" >春</li>\n    <li>夏</li>\n    <li>秋</li>\n    <li>冬</li>\n</ul><figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>  <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"square\"</span> &gt;</span>春<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span>夏<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span>秋<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span>冬<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id=\"有序列表-ol\">有序列表 ol<a href=\"#有序列表-ol\" title=\"有序列表 ol\"></a></h2><ul><li>每对<code>&lt;ol&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;</code>中至少应包含一对<code>&lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;</code>。</li>\n<li>有序列表中，除了<code>type</code>属性之外，还可以为<code>&lt;ol&gt;</code>定义<code>start</code>属性、为<code>&lt;li&gt;</code>定义<code>value</code>属性。</li>\n</ul><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/dxsummer/cdn/img/html/20201025174742.png\" style=\"zoom: 80%;\" /><h2 id=\"定义列表\">定义列表<a href=\"#定义列表\" title=\"定义列表\"></a></h2><ul><li>定义列表常用于图文混排，其中<code>&lt;dt&gt;&lt;/dt&gt;</code>标签中插入图片，<code>&lt;dd&gt;&lt;/dd&gt;</code>标签中放入对图片解释说明的文字。</li>\n<li><code>&lt;dl&gt;</code> <code>&lt;dt&gt;</code> <code>&lt;dd&gt;</code> 3个标签之间不允许出现其他标签</li>\n<li><mark><code>&lt;dl&gt;</code> 必须与<code>&lt;dt&gt;</code>相邻</mark></li>\n</ul><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/dxsummer/cdn/img/html/20201025175351.png\" class=\"φcy\"></p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/dxsummer/cdn/img/html/20201025175526.png\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" /><h2 id=\"列表的嵌套\">列表的嵌套<a href=\"#列表的嵌套\" title=\"列表的嵌套\"></a></h2><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/dxsummer/cdn/img/html/20201025214813.png\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" /><figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">h2</span>&gt;</span>饮品<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">h2</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span>咖啡</span><br><span class=\"line\">    \t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">ol</span>&gt;</span>                    <span class=\"comment\">&lt;!--有序列表的嵌套--&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        \t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span>拿铁<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            \t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span>摩卡<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        \t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">ol</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">     <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span>茶</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">ul</span>&gt;</span>                     <span class=\"comment\">&lt;!--无序列表的嵌套--&gt;</span> </span><br><span class=\"line\">        \t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span>碧螺春<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            \t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span>龙井<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id=\"css控制列表样式\">CSS控制列表样式<a href=\"#css控制列表样式\" title=\"CSS控制列表样式\"></a></h1><p>定义<strong>无序或有序列表</strong>时，可以通过<strong>标签的属性</strong>控制列表的<strong>项目符号</strong>，但是这种方式实现的效果并不理想，因此需要使用CSS中的<strong>列表样式属性</strong>。</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/dxsummer/cdn/img/html/20201025215909.png\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" /><h2 id=\"list-style-type\">list-style-type<a href=\"#list-style-type\" title=\"list-style-type\"></a></h2><ul><li>因为各个浏览器对list-style-type属性的解析不同。因此，在实际网页制作过程中不推荐使用   list-style-type属性。</li>\n</ul><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/dxsummer/cdn/img/html/20201025215934.png\" style=\"zoom: 67%;\" /><h2 id=\"list-style-image\">list-style-image<a href=\"#list-style-image\" title=\"list-style-image\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-tag\">ul</span>&#123;<span class=\"attribute\">list-style-image</span>:<span class=\"built_in\">url</span>(图片路径);&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/dxsummer/cdn/img/html/20201025220326.png\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" /><figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;style type=\"text/css\"&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-tag\">ul</span>&#123;<span class=\"attribute\">list-style-image</span>:<span class=\"built_in\">url</span>(images/book.png);&#125;  </span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/style&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id=\"list-style-position\">list-style-position<a href=\"#list-style-position\" title=\"list-style-position\"></a></h2><ul><li><code>inside</code>：列表项目符号位于列表文本以内。</li>\n<li><code>outside</code>：列表项目符号位于列表文本以外。</li>\n</ul><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/dxsummer/cdn/img/html/20201025220644.png\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" /><figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;style type=\"text/css\"&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.in</span>&#123;<span class=\"attribute\">list-style-position</span>:inside;&#125;   </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.out</span>&#123;<span class=\"attribute\">list-style-psition</span>:outside;&#125; </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-tag\">li</span>&#123; <span class=\"attribute\">border</span>:<span class=\"number\">1px</span> solid <span class=\"number\">#CCC</span>;&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/style&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id=\"list-style-复合属性\">list-style 复合属性<a href=\"#list-style-复合属性\" title=\"list-style 复合属性\"></a></h2><ul><li>在实际网页制作过程中，为了更高效地控制列表项目符号，通常将<code>list-style</code>的属性值定义为<code>none</code>，然后通过为<code>&lt;li&gt;</code>设置背景图像的方式实现不同的列表项目符号。</li>\n</ul><figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-tag\">list-style</span>:列表项目符号 列表项目符号的位置 列表项目图像;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id=\"链接\">链接<a href=\"#链接\" title=\"链接\"></a></h1><h2 id=\"超链接\">超链接<a href=\"#超链接\" title=\"超链接\"></a></h2><ul><li>通过超链接，实现页面之间的跳转</li>\n<li><code>href</code>用于指定链接目标的<code>url</code>地址，当为<code>&lt;a&gt;</code>标签应用<code>href</code>属性时，它就具有了超链接的功能。</li>\n<li><code>target</code>：用于指定链接页面的打开方式，其取值有<code>_self</code>和<code>_blank</code>两种，其中<strong><code>_self</code>为默认值，意为在原窗口中打开，<code>_blank</code>为在新窗口中打开。</strong></li>\n</ul><figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;a href=\"跳转目标\" target=\"目标窗口的弹出方式\"&gt;文本或图像&lt;/a&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>1、暂时没有确定链接目标时，通常将<code>&lt;a&gt;</code>标签的<code>href</code>属性值定义为“<code>#</code>” (即<code>href=&quot;#&quot;</code>)，表示该链接暂时为一个空链接。<br>2、不仅可以创建<strong>文本超链接</strong>，在网页中各种网页元素，如<strong>图像、 表格、音频、视频</strong>等都可以添加超链接。<br>3、<strong>当给图像添加超链接时，图像会自动加上边框</strong>，通常需要<strong>清除超链接图像的边框</strong>。</p>\n<h2 id=\"锚点链接\">锚点链接<a href=\"#锚点链接\" title=\"锚点链接\"></a></h2><ul><li>通过创建锚点链接，用户能够快速定位到目标内容。</li>\n</ul><p><strong><font color=\"red\" >创建锚点步骤</font></strong></p>\n<ol><li>使用“<code>&lt;a href=&quot;#id名&quot;&gt;链接文本&lt;/a&gt;</code>”创建链接文本</li>\n<li>使用相应的<code>id</code>名标注跳转目标的位置</li>\n</ol><figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;a href=\"#one\"&gt;平面广告设计&lt;/a&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">.</span><br><span class=\"line\">.</span><br><span class=\"line\">.</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;h3 id=\"one\"&gt;平面广告设计&lt;/h3&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id=\"链接伪类\">链接伪类<a href=\"#链接伪类\" title=\"链接伪类\"></a></h2><ul><li>定义超链接时，为了提高用户体验，经常需要为超链接指定不同的状态，使得超链接在点击前、点击后和鼠标悬停时的样式不同。</li>\n<li>在CSS中通过<strong>链接伪类</strong>可以实现<strong>不同的链接状态</strong></li>\n<li>伪类并不是真正意义上的类，它的名称是由系统定义的，通常由<strong>标签名、类名或id名加“<code>：</code>”构成</strong>。</li>\n</ul><div class=\"φcz\"><div class=\"φdb\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th>超链接标签<code>&lt;a&gt;</code>的伪类</th><th><strong>含义</strong></th></tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td><code>a:link{ CSS样式规则; }</code></td><td>未访问时超链接的状态</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>a:visited{ CSS样式规则; }</code></td><td>访问后超链接的状态</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>a:hover{ CSS样式规则; }</code></td><td>鼠标经过、悬停时超链接的状态</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code>a:active{ CSS样式规则; }</code></td><td>鼠标点击不动时超链接的状态</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></div></div><ul><li><p><mark>同时使用链接的4种伪类时，通常按照<code>a:link</code>、<code>a:visited</code>、<code>a:hover</code>和<code>a:active</code>的顺序书写，否则定义的样式可能不起作用。</mark></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>除了文本样式之外，链接伪类还常常用于<strong>控制超链接的背景</strong>、<strong>边框等样式</strong>。</p>\n</li>\n</ul><figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;style type=\"text/css\"&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-tag\">a</span><span class=\"selector-pseudo\">:link</span>,<span class=\"selector-tag\">a</span><span class=\"selector-pseudo\">:visited</span>&#123;\t<span class=\"comment\">/*未访问和访问后*/</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"attribute\">color</span>:<span class=\"number\">#FC0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"attribute\">text-decoration</span>:none;         <span class=\"comment\">/*清除超链接默认的下划线*/</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"attribute\">margin-right</span>:<span class=\"number\">20px</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-tag\">a</span><span class=\"selector-pseudo\">:hover</span>&#123;                             </span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"attribute\">color</span>:<span class=\"number\">#0F0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"attribute\">text-decoration</span>:underline;  <span class=\"comment\">/*鼠标悬停时出现下划线*/</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-tag\">a</span><span class=\"selector-pseudo\">:active</span>&#123; <span class=\"attribute\">color</span>:<span class=\"number\">#F00</span>;&#125;            </span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/style&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","prev":{"title":"导航栏","link":"posts/25281569"},"next":{"title":"串、数组和广义表","link":"posts/32c38e43"},"plink":"https://dxsummer.gitee.io/posts/9a7f11f9/","toc":[{"id":"列表标签","title":"列表标签","index":"1","children":[{"id":"无序列表-ul","title":"无序列表 ul","index":"1.1"},{"id":"有序列表-ol","title":"有序列表 ol","index":"1.2"},{"id":"定义列表","title":"定义列表","index":"1.3"},{"id":"列表的嵌套","title":"列表的嵌套","index":"1.4"}]},{"id":"css控制列表样式","title":"CSS控制列表样式","index":"2","children":[{"id":"list-style-type","title":"list-style-type","index":"2.1"},{"id":"list-style-image","title":"list-style-image","index":"2.2"},{"id":"list-style-position","title":"list-style-position","index":"2.3"},{"id":"list-style-复合属性","title":"list-style 复合属性","index":"2.4"}]},{"id":"链接","title":"链接","index":"3","children":[{"id":"超链接","title":"超链接","index":"3.1"},{"id":"锚点链接","title":"锚点链接","index":"3.2"},{"id":"链接伪类","title":"链接伪类","index":"3.3"}]}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"DxSummer","link":"<a href=\"https://dxsummer.gitee.io/posts/9a7f11f9/\" title=\"列表和超链接\">https://dxsummer.gitee.io/posts/9a7f11f9/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\\\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\\\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","published":"2020年10月25日","updated":"2020年10月25日"}}